rg/resource/C\\u00e9sar_Cielo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cielo set his world record of 20.91 during swimming's so-called \\\"super suit\\\" era in 2009.\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 769, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 680, \"end\": 685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daewoo_LeMans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.193055049914061e-14, \"text\": \"Cielo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daewoo_LeMans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daewoo_LeMans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those suits were later banned because they increased buoyancy and reduced drag, resulting in nearly 150 world records falling in 2009 before being prohibited in 2010.\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 936, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I knew I had a chance to do a PB (personal best),\\\" McEvoy said.\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 1002, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My old PB was 21.06, so maybe 20.99?\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1040, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1011, \"end\": 1013, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Byte\", \"score\": 0.9999999999888587, \"rank\": 1.1121839981108746e-11, \"text\": \"PB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Byte\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Byte\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But doing \\u206020.88 is unreal.\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\": 1068, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's crazy.\\\"\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1081, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cielo wasquick to congratulateMcEvoy on social media, tweeting: \\\"Congrats, Cam.\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1162, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1083, \"end\": 1088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daewoo_LeMans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.193055049914061e-14, \"text\": \"Cielo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daewoo_LeMans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daewoo_LeMans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lightning fast swim!\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1183, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Incredib